'''''Star Wars Insider'' 49''' is the forty-ninth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands the week of [[May 15]], [[2000]]. This issue celebrated the twentieth anniversary of the [[original trilogy]] film [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']]. As such, the design for issue 49 took its inspiration from the [[1980]] publication ''[[Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back - Official Collectors Edition]]''.

